tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE website_traffic_data (
  visitor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  page_visited VARCHAR(255),
  referrer VARCHAR(255),
  conversion BOOLEAN
)

CREATE TABLE website_traffic_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    page_url VARCHAR,
    visitor_id INT,
    visit_duration INT,
    visit_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE website_traffic_data (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  date TIMESTAMP,
  page_url VARCHAR(255),
  visitor_id INT,
  browser VARCHAR(50),
  time_spent_seconds INT
)

CREATE TABLE marketing_strategies (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  strategy_name VARCHAR(100),
  target_audience VARCHAR(100),
  conversion_rate DECIMAL(5,2),
  campaign_budget DECIMAL(10,2),
  start_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE web_traffic_analysis (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  page_url VARCHAR(255),
  total_visits INT,
  unique_visitors INT,
  bounce_rate DECIMAL(5,2),
  average_time_spent_seconds INT
)

CREATE TABLE website_visits (
    visit_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    visitor_id UUID,
    visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    page_visited TEXT,
    referral_source TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE visitor_details (
    visitor_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    visitor_name TEXT,
    visitor_email TEXT,
    first_visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    last_visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE page_data (
    page_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    page_url TEXT,
    page_title TEXT,
    average_visit_duration INTERVAL,
    total_visits INT
);

CREATE TABLE referral_sources (
    source_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    source_name TEXT,
    source_type TEXT,
    source_category TEXT,
    total_visits INT
);

CREATE TABLE website_visits (
  visit_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  visitor_id INT,
  visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  page_visited VARCHAR,
  duration_minutes INT
)

CREATE TABLE visitor_info (
  visitor_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  visitor_name VARCHAR,
  visitor_email VARCHAR,
  visit_count INT,
  first_visit TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE page_metadata (
  page_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  page_url VARCHAR,
  page_title VARCHAR,
  meta_tags JSON,
  page_views INT
)

CREATE TABLE referral_sources (
  source_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  source_name VARCHAR,
  traffic_type VARCHAR,
  referrals INT
)

CREATE TABLE conversion_rates (
  conversion_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  conversion_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  converted_visitor_id INT,
  conversion_page VARCHAR,
  conversion_value DECIMAL
)
